'''Elena''' is the girlfriend of [[Jake Weitzman]].

==History==
Elena came into the hospital when her boyfriend, Jake, was there to be separated from his twin brother, Pete. While she was there, Jake discovered that Elena and Pete had a relationship beyond his with her. He asked Elena to choose and was upset when Elena didn't choose him.

After they were separated, she went to see Pete, but he seemed disinterested in seeing her.

==Relationships==
===Romantic===
She was dating [[Jake Weitzman]]. Despite that, she also had feelings for Jake's brother, [[Peter Weitzman|Pete]]. They would often talk after Jake fell asleep and Elena liked it that Pete stood up for her against Jake.
